## Running Tests

```bash
# Run all tests
pytest

# Run with coverage
pytest --cov=todo

# Run specific test file
pytest tests/test_smoke.py
```

## Code Quality

```bash
# Format code
black src/ tests/

# Lint code
flake8 src/ tests/
```

